# coding: utf-8
#!python

import numpy
import pyNN.brainscales as sim
from pyNN.random import RandomDistribution

sim.setup()

pop_2 = sim.Population(1, sim.IF_curr_alpha(v_rest=-65 , cm=1 , tau_m=20 , tau_refrac=0 , tau_syn_E=5 , tau_syn_I=5 , i_offset=0 , v_reset=-65 , v_thresh=-50 )
pop_3 = sim.Population(1, sim.IF_curr_alpha(v_rest=-65 , cm=1 , tau_m=20 , tau_refrac=0 , tau_syn_E=5 , tau_syn_I=5 , i_offset=0 , v_reset=-65 , v_thresh=-50 )
pop_4 = sim.Population(1, sim.IF_curr_alpha(v_rest=-65 , cm=1 , tau_m=20 , tau_refrac=0 , tau_syn_E=5 , tau_syn_I=5 , i_offset=0 , v_reset=-65 , v_thresh=-50 )
sim.Projection(pop_2, pop_2, sim.AllToAllConnector(), sim.StaticSynapse())
pop_3.initialize(v=-65 , isyn_exc=3 , isyn_inh=0 , label=Pop3)


sim.run(10)

io_2 = NixIO("U_pop_2.nix", "ow")
pop_2.write_data("io_2")
io_3 = NixIO("U_pop_3.nix", "ow")
pop_3.write_data("io_3")
io_4 = NixIO("U_pop_4.nix", "ow")
pop_4.write_data("io_4")
io_5 = NixIO("U_pop_5.nix", "ow")
pop_5.write_data("io_5")


sim.end()
